title: Giving you some Me Time - Rentals in Weston. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Located in the beautiful gated community of "The Lakes" at the end of a cul-de-sac.', ' This bright clean home features 3 Bedrooms and 2.5 Bathrooms with keyless entry.', ' Say goodbye to keys!', ' Brand new Luxury floors throughout, Granite kitchen tops, stainless appliances, kitchen opens to family room with relaxing lake views.', 'NEW BATHROOMS INSTALLED AUGUST 1,2022.', 'Screened in covered porch looks out onto the lake, 2 car garage and lots of driveway space.', 'Enjoy the spacious yard and lawn area right outside your back door.', ' Close to  schools, shopping, banking and walking trails.', ' Community pool and park area for extra fun!', 'Available August 15, 2022', '***', 'Text Message MALKA to', 'show contact info', 'For  Details & Pics Of This Property***', 'Brought to you by Malka Espiedra at Weichert, Realtors® - Capella Estates - Weston']
